						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of 7 <hi rend="italic">tuḷaippoṉ</hi> of gold for a perpetual lamp in the temple of Perumānadigaḷ at Tirunalakkuṉṟam in Kuṉṟiyūr-nāḍu by <hi rend="bold">Poduva••••Echchiḻ Maṇḍai</hi> a resident <hi rend="bold">of Perunkūṟṟakkuḍi</hi> in the same <hi rend="italic">nāḍu</hi>, who deposited the amount with four temple servants <hi rend="italic">(paṭṭuḍaiyār)</hi> for the purpose.</p>						

						</summary>
